十二月主义者宣布推出新双专辑《As It Ever Was, So It Will Be Again》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-decemberists-announce-new-double-album-as-it-ever-was-so-it-will-be-again-preorder-3603568?utm_source= rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=the-decemberists-announce-new-double-album-as-it-ever-so-it-will-be-again-preorderLiberty Dunworth Tue, 19 Mar 2024 16:45:23 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndieProg https://www.nme.com/?p=3603568 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Decemberists@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="十二月党人，2024" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Decemberists@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Decemberists@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Decemberists@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Decemberists@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Decemberists@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Decemberists@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>他们还分享了 19 分钟的单曲《Joan In The Garden》</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-decemberists-announce-new-double-album-as-it-ever-was-so-it-will-be-again-preorder-3603568">The Decemberists 宣布新双专辑《As It Ever Was, So It Will Be Again》的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Decemberists@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="十二月党人，2024" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Decemberists@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Decemberists@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Decemberists@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Decemberists@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Decemberists@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Decemberists@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-decemberists">Decemberists</a>回来了，并分享了一张名为“As It Ever Was, So It Will Be Again”的全新专辑的详细信息。看看下面的 proggy 新单曲。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <b><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-decemberists-on-life-in-trumps-america-and-the-trouble-with-being-a-morrissey-fan-2270054">十二月党人谈特朗普治下的美国生活，以及成为莫里西粉丝的麻烦</a></b></strong></li></ul><p>这张新唱片于今天（3 月 19 日）发布，标志着该乐队的第九张录音室专辑，也是自中断六年以来的第一张专辑。</p><p> 《As It Ever Was, So It Will Be Again》将被打造为一张双专辑，由主唱 Colin Meloy 和 Tucker Martine 制作，并与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-shins">The</a>等众多明星合作。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-shins">Shins</a>的 James Mercer 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rem">REM</a>的 Mike Mills。</p><p>该歌曲定于 6 月 14 日通过 YABB Records（三十只老虎）发行，今天乐队分享了这首有趣的新单曲——一首长达 19 分钟的前卫摇滚史诗，名为“Joan In The Garden”。</p><p> “自从‘我会成为你的女孩’会议以来，‘花园里的琼’一直是一个想法，”梅洛伊谈到这首歌的灵感时说道。 “读完莉迪亚·尤克纳维奇（Lydia Yuknavitch）美丽的垃圾小说<em>《贞德之书》</em>后，我迷上了圣女贞德。我想制作我自己版本的琼——但是这首歌既讲述了创作过程，也讲述了真实的女人，讲述了天使般的拜访和创造性的拜访，以及两者的致幻品质。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="十二月党人 - 花园里的琼（官方音频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/6nhLuHWcTdo?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>根据一份新的新闻稿，《As It Ever Was, So It Will Be Again》不仅将成为十二月党迄今为止分享的最长的专辑，而且也希望成为他们最有同理心和最容易理解的专辑。</p><p> “这 13 首歌就像是我们忧虑的时代和微弱希望的相互认可的信号。 《收割者》中存在主义的艰辛和资本主义的烦恼，《美国造就我》中鸦片般的迷幻和混乱的沙文主义，《我想要的就是你》的朴实温柔和绝对投降：《一如既往》是救赎的证明乐队通过同时重温几种旧模式来寻找新的集体赞美诗，”它写道。</p><p> “梅洛伊会自豪地告诉你，这是十二月主义者最好的专辑——甚至可能是 22 年工作的最终实现。 《既往如是，亦复如是》听起来充满了现在的紧迫感和热情，也许比以往任何时候都更加紧迫。”</p><p>这一消息也是在乐队上个月回归后发布的，并通过放弃单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-decemberists-share-first-new-song-in-six-years-burial-ground-featuring-the-shins-james-mercer-3583747">“Burial Ground”</a>来预告一张新专辑。</p><p>在下面找到完整的曲目列表和专辑封面。<a href="https://orcd.co/aiewsiwba" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此</a>预订专辑。 </p><figure id="attachment_3603573" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3603573" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3603573" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Decemberists-Artwork@2000x2000.jpg" alt="Decemberists 专辑《As It Ever Was, So It Will Be Again》" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Decemberists-Artwork@2000x2000.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Decemberists-Artwork@2000x2000-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Decemberists-Artwork@2000x2000-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Decemberists-Artwork@2000x2000-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Decemberists-Artwork@2000x2000-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Decemberists-Artwork@2000x2000-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Decemberists-Artwork@2000x2000-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3603573" class="wp-caption-text"> Decemberists 的《As It Ever Was, So It Will Be Again》专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><h2><strong>“一如既往，所以会再次”曲目列表是：</strong></h2><p> <strong>1.“墓地”</strong><br /> <strong>2.“哦不！”</strong><br /> <strong>3.《收割者》</strong><br /> <strong>4.“长白面纱”</strong><br /> <strong>5.“威廉·菲茨威廉”</strong><br /> <strong>6.“不要去树林”</strong><br /> <strong>7.《黑玛丽亚》</strong><br /> <strong>8.《我想要的只是你》</strong><br /> <strong>9.“为早晨而生”</strong><br /> <strong>10.“美国造就了我”</strong><br /> <strong>11.“告诉我你在想什么”</strong><br /> <strong>12.“永不满足”</strong><br /> <strong>13.《琼在花园里》</strong></p><p>除了新专辑之外，The Decemberists 还计划在春季和夏季进行<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-decemberists-announce-north-american-tour-for-august-2022-3146525">广泛的北美巡演</a>。巡演于 4 月 30 日在纽约州金斯顿的阿尔斯特表演艺术中心开始，并于 8 月在西海岸结束。</p><p>梅洛伊等人还将于 8 月 25 日<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/all-points-east">在伦敦 All Point East</a>演出。请访问<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fthe-decemberists-tickets%2Fartist%2F882946" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>获取美国门票， <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fthe-decemberists-tickets%2Fartist%2F882946" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>访问英国门票。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-decemberists-announce-new-double-album-as-it-ever-was-so-it-will-be-again-preorder-3603568">The Decemberists 宣布新双专辑《As It Ever Was, So It Will Be Again》的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
