、 <a href="/artists/hozier">Hozier</a> 、 <a href="/artists/sza">SZA</a> 、 <a href="/artists/the-killers">The Killers</a>等乐队已被宣布为今年<a href="https://www.nme.com/tags/lollapalooza">Lollapalooza</a>的头条新闻。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/lollapalooza-2023-review-the-chicago-mainstay-once-again-hits-the-music-festival-sweet-spot-3480133">Lollapalooza 2023 回顾：芝加哥中流砥柱再次成为音乐节的最佳选择</a></strong></li></ul><p>其他将成为今年芝加哥年度音乐节主角的乐队包括<a href="/artists/future">Future</a> x <a href="/artists/metro-boomin">Metro Boomin</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Stray-Kids">Stray Kids</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Melanie-Martinez">Melanie Martinez</a>和<a href="/artists/skrillex">Skrillex</a> 。 Lollapalooza 将于 8 月 1 日至 4 日返回其主场格兰特公园。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/the-cover"><em>NME</em>封面</a>校友<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-cover/the-cover-been-stellar-interview-scream-from-new-york-ny-3599283">Been Stellar</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-cover/the-cover-geese-3d-country-3454434">Geese</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-cover/the-cover-the-last-dinner-party-interview-prelude-to-ecstasy-3552625">The Last Evening Party</a>等人也将与<a href="/artists/deftones">Deftones</a> 、 <a href="/artists/tate-mcrae">Tate McRae</a> 、 <a href="/artists/laufey">Laufey</a> （与芝加哥爱乐乐团合作）、 <a href="/artists/conan-grey">Conan Gray</a> 、 <a href="/artists/renee-rapp">Reneé Rapp</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Faye-Webster">Faye Webster</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Victoria-Monet">Victoria Monet</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Sexyy-Red">Sexyy Red</a>一起演出。 、 泰迪·游泳、 本森·布恩、<a href="/artists/jungle">丛林</a>、<a href="/artists/two-door-cinema-club">两门电影俱乐部</a>、<a href="/artists/killer-mike">杀手迈克</a>、<a href="/artists/vince-staples">文斯·斯台普斯</a>、<a href="/artists/Four-Tet">四四人</a>、<a href="/artists/Kevin-Abstract">凯文·抽象</a>、<a href="/artists/Ethel-Cain">埃塞尔·凯恩</a>、<a href="/artists/chappell-roan">查</a>佩尔·罗恩、 蒂兹达阵、<a href="/artists/Kenny-Beats">肯尼·</a>贝茨、<a href="/artists/the-japanese-house">日本之家</a>、<a href="/artists/romy">罗密</a>、<a href="/artists/flo">弗洛</a>、 邪教、<a href="/artists/slow-pulp">慢纸浆</a>、<a href="/artists/Militarie-Gun">军用枪</a>、血肉、小精灵等等。</p><p>通过 Lollapalooza 官方网站注册预售密码的人即可享受节日通行证预售。这将保证球迷以最低价格获得 4 天的门票。预售将于 3 月 21 日星期四上午 10 点至中午 12 点（中部时间）（格林威治标准时间凌晨 3 点至凌晨 5 点）开始。一旦公开发售开始，价格将于 3 月 21 日中部时间中午 12 点（格林威治标准时间上午 5 点）上涨。 </p><figure id="attachment_3603571" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3603571" style="width: 2350px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3603571" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Lollapalooza-2024-line-up-poster.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="Lollapalooza 2024 年阵容海报。图片来源：新闻界" width="2350" height="2938" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Lollapalooza-2024-line-up-poster.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2350w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Lollapalooza-2024-line-up-poster.-Credit-PRESS-400x500.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Lollapalooza-2024-line-up-poster.-Credit-PRESS-800x1000.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Lollapalooza-2024-line-up-poster.-Credit-PRESS-696x870.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Lollapalooza-2024-line-up-poster.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1740.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Lollapalooza-2024-line-up-poster.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1335.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2350px) 100vw, 2350px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3603571" class="wp-caption-text"> Lollapalooza 2024 年阵容海报。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>单日票以及逐日排队将在稍后提供。八岁及以下的儿童将可以与持票成人一起免费参加，并享受 Kidzapalooza，这是节日期间的互动音乐游乐场，提供一系列适合家庭的表演、活动、音乐和舞蹈工作坊等。</p><p>去年版本的 Lollapalooza 见证了<a href="/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a> 、 <a href="/artists/karol-g">Karol G</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Kendrick-Lamar">Kendrick Lamar</a> 、 <a href="/artists/the-1975">The 1975</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Holly-Humberstone">Holly Humberstone</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Sabrina-Carpenter">Sabrina Carpenter</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Foals">Foaals</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Red-Hot-Chili-Peppers">Red Hot Chili Peppers</a>等人的表演。</p><p>在对<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/lollapalooza-2023-review-the-chicago-mainstay-once-again-hits-the-music-festival-sweet-spot-3480133">2023 年 Lollapalooza 音乐节的五星级评论</a>中， <em>NME</em>分享道：“但即使在音乐节上竭尽全力的表演者中，仍然存在着一种不完美的暗流，这使得一切变得平易近人、真实。 Lollapalooza 并没有试图成为任何人，每年都会带着新的计划回归，优先考虑声音的多样性，并坚定地致力于突出新鲜的表演（比如在 BMI 舞台上，崭露头角的表演如安妮·迪鲁索 (Annie DiRusso) 和《美容学校辍学》(Beauty School Dropout) 与粉丝们见面，他们每一个字都跟着唱）音乐节证明了其致力于将音乐放在第一位，而 Lollapalooza 的粉丝们也反映了这种努力。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blink-182-hozier-tyler-the-creator-and-more-lead-lollapalooza-2024-line-up-3603543">Blink-182 后、Hozier、Tyler、The Creator 等 Lollapalooza 2024 领军阵容</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
芭芭拉·史翠珊 (Barbra Streisand) 发表声明后，埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 颁奖典礼被取消https://www.nme.com/news/film/elon-musk-leadership-award-cancelled-barbra-streisand-complain-3603536?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=elon-musk-leadership-award-cancelled-barbra-史翠珊-抱怨Alex BerryTue, 19 Mar 2024 16:06:54 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3603536 <p><img width="1891" height="1201" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Elon-Musk-Leadership.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="埃隆·马斯克" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Elon-Musk-Leadership.jpg 1891w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Elon-Musk-Leadership-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Elon-Musk-Leadership-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Elon-Musk-Leadership-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Elon-Musk-Leadership-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Elon-Musk-Leadership-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1891px) 100vw, 1891px" /></p><p>该活动还旨在纪念鲁珀特·默多克</p><p>芭芭拉·史翠珊 (Barbra Streisand) 的声明首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/elon-musk-leadership-award-cancelled-barbra-streisand-complain-3603536">后，埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 的颁奖典礼被取消</a>。</p> ; <p><img width="1891" height="1201" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Elon-Musk-Leadership.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="埃隆·马斯克" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Elon-Musk-Leadership.jpg 1891w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Elon-Musk-Leadership-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Elon-Musk-Leadership-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Elon-Musk-Leadership-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Elon-Musk-Leadership-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Elon-Musk-Leadership-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1891px) 100vw, 1891px" /></p><p>由于知名人士的投诉，一场旨在纪念<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elon-musk">埃隆·马斯克</a>和鲁珀特·默多克等人的活动已被取消。</p><p> 3 月 13 日宣布，今年奥珀曼基金会大法官露丝·巴德·金斯伯格领导奖的获奖者包括马斯克、默多克、玛莎·斯图尔特、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sylvester-stallone">西尔维斯特·史泰龙</a>和迈克尔·米尔肯。</p><p>这位特斯拉创始人和前福克斯新闻首席执行官的加入引发了金斯伯格家族成员的强烈反对。金斯伯格的儿子詹姆斯批评了该基金会，称他的母亲会对获奖者感到“震惊”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3603548" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3603548" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3603548" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ruth-Bader-Ginsburg-Elon-Musk.jpg" alt="露丝·巴德·金斯伯格" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ruth-Bader-Ginsburg-Elon-Musk.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ruth-Bader-Ginsburg-Elon-Musk-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ruth-Bader-Ginsburg-Elon-Musk-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ruth-Bader-Ginsburg-Elon-Musk-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ruth-Bader-Ginsburg-Elon-Musk-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ruth-Bader-Ginsburg-Elon-Musk-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3603548" class="wp-caption-text">露丝·巴德·金斯伯格于 2019 年 9 月 12 日在华盛顿特区。图片来源：盖蒂/汤姆·布伦纳/盖蒂图片社拍摄</figcaption></figure><p>金斯伯格告诉<a href="https://edition.cnn.com/2024/03/17/politics/ruth-bader-ginsburg-son-award-rupert-murdoch-elon-musk/index.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>美国有线电视新闻网</em></a>：“当你想到努力创建一个更加公正的社会时，这当然是妈妈的最终目标，你可能会想到这些姓氏。”</p><p>他称这一消息是“对[他]母亲记忆的亵渎”，并说：“我认为她会感到震惊。”</p><p>昨天（3月18日）<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/barbra-streisand">芭芭拉·史翠珊</a>在 Instagram 上表达了对金斯伯格家族的支持，并与他们一起谴责了颁奖典礼获奖者的选择。</p><p>回顾去年获得最高法院大法官索尼娅·索托马约尔的荣誉，史翠珊写道：“金斯伯格大法官和索托马约尔大法官是两位最受尊敬的女性榜样，她们对民主价值观、特别是妇女权利的承诺是无与伦比的。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C4quvPaL4fg/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67