ull wp-post-image" alt="罗杰·达尔特雷 (Roger Daltrey) 和皮特·汤森德 (Pete Townshend) 与 The Who 一起在舞台上现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/TheWho-Teenage-Cancer-Trust-London-Royal-Albert-Hall-orchestral-show-news.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/TheWho-Teenage-Cancer-Trust-London-Royal-Albert-Hall-orchestral-show-news-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/TheWho-Teenage-Cancer-Trust-London-Royal-Albert-Hall-orchestral-show-news-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/TheWho-Teenage-Cancer-Trust-London-Royal-Albert-Hall-orchestral-show-news-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/TheWho-Teenage-Cancer-Trust-London-Royal-Albert-Hall-orchestral-show-news-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/TheWho-Teenage-Cancer-Trust-London-Royal-Albert-Hall-orchestral-show-news-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>昨晚（3 月 18 日）， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-who">The Who 乐队</a>以一场特别的管弦乐表演拉开了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-the-chemical-brothers-and-young-fathers-to-play-2024-teenage-cancer-trust-gigs-3566977">在伦敦举行的 2024 年青少年癌症信托基金会系列音乐会的序幕</a>。请参阅下面的片段、图像和完整的歌单。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/roger-daltrey-on-teenage-cancer-trust-and-the-chances-of-new-music-from-the-who-3410696">罗杰·达尔特雷 (Roger Daltrey) 谈论青少年癌症信托基金以及 The Who 推出新音乐的机会</a></strong></li></ul><p>今年由 The Who 主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/roger-daltrey">Roger Daltrey</a>策划的慈善年度演出将于本周在历史悠久的皇家阿尔伯特音乐厅举行，诺埃尔·加拉格尔<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallaghers-high-flying-birds">(Noel Gallagher) 的 High Flying Birds</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-chemical-brothers">The Chemical Brothers</a>等乐队也将参加演出。</p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/squeeze">Squeeze</a>的开场演出之后，昨天的观众欣赏了 The Who 2024 年的首场现场表演。这个标志性乐队带来了 21 首曲目，其中包括管弦乐曲，中间有一个“仅限乐队”的部分。</p><p> “它为这些演出注入了活力，带来了捐款，”吉他手皮特<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pete-townshend">·汤森德（Pete Townshend）</a>在晚上的某个时刻说道，“当然，就是你买票。我们很感激。”</p><p>音乐会以《我无法解释》开始，随后管弦乐演奏了《谁人》1969 年摇滚歌剧专辑《汤米》中的几首片段，包括《弹球巫师》、《序曲》和《我们不会接受它》 &#39;。</p><p>后来，“仅限乐队”的节目播放了“孩子们都很好”、“我的一代”、“不会再次被愚弄”、“蓝眼睛背后”等。</p><p>随后，乐团凯旋归来，带来了最后一首乐曲，包括《The Real Me》、《I&#39;m One》、《5.15》、《The Rock》、《Love, Reign O&#39;er Me》和《Baba O&#39;Reilly》 &#39;。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="谁人@皇家阿尔伯特音乐厅：不会再被愚弄 |青少年癌症信托基金 | 18-03-2024 西伦敦" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/BLQV8MxL_Zk?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="谁人@皇家阿尔伯特音乐厅：替补|青少年癌症信托基金 | 18-03-2024 西伦敦" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/NhD_8eHtUsY?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><figure id="attachment_3603509" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3603509" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3603509" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/TheWho-London-2024-4.jpg" alt="谁人乐队 (The Who) 在伦敦皇家阿尔伯特音乐厅举行的 2024 年青少年癌症信托基金会系列音乐会上现场表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/TheWho-London-2024-4.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/TheWho-London-2024-4-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/TheWho-London-2024-4-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/TheWho-London-2024-4-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/TheWho-London-2024-4-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/TheWho-London-2024-4-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(m